quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  4,71,"Enywe abasuubila, mube meso! Ne murule mumukanda nohomba murule mwesi halala"
  4,72,"Ne aliwo mwinywe owulatong’a inyuma, ne nimunyoolwa namasila aboola mbu; “Nyasaye yakholele obulayi shembele ninabo tawe.”"
  4,73,Ne nimunyoola tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye aboola mbu - bili shinga abuyanzi nibulali hakari wenyu ni naye tawe- “ abayie manayanga emba halala ninabo ndabura okhubura okhukhongo.”
  4,74,"Kho mana khuye khunjila ya Nyasaye balia bakusinjia obulamu bwokhushialo, nende mwikulu ( Akhera.) Ne ukhuyana khunjila ya Nyasaye mana yerwe nohomba ashile, khwitsa okhumurunga omurungo omukhongo"
  4,75,"Muli murie amulakhupananga khunjila ya Nyasaye nende yabalia baranjilwe Abasatsa Nabakhasi nende Abana ababoolanga mbu : “Nyasaye wefu omulesi, khurusie mulukongo luno alwa Abandu balwo ni ababii, ne okhurerele Omuliindi okhurula khwiwe ne okhuhelesie Omuhabini urulanga khwiwe.”"
  4,76,"Balia abasuubila balwananga khunjila ya Nyasaye, ne balia abakhaya balwanilanga khunjila yobukori, kho lwane nende abetsa ba shetani. Toto abukaati bwa shetani nobuteshele"